								<div class="info-item">
									<strong>Element:</strong> None
								</div>
								<div class="info-item">
									<strong>Zones:</strong> Canopy Heights, Forest Valley
								</div>
								<div class="info-item">
									<strong>Behavior:</strong> Skittish glider, opportunistic snatcher, aerial nuisance
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="creature-section">
								<h4>📖 Lore</h4>
								<p>Skyvine Drakes are small, vine-colored gliding reptiles that dart between branches in the upper canopy. They are agile, curious, and occasionally bold enough to swoop down and snatch food, trinkets, or even crafting components from unwary hunters.</p>
								<p>Though individually weak, their mobility makes them disruptive. They rarely fight to kill—Skyvine Drakes attack only to create distance or distract larger predators. When startled, several may scatter at once, raining leaves and debris down as they flee.</p>
								<p>They are easy prey when grounded… but catching one is the real challenge.</p>
							</div>

							<div class="creature-section">
								<h4>📊 Stats & Attributes</h4>
								<div class="stats-grid">
									<div class="stat-block">
										<div class="stat-row"><span>STR</span><strong>2 (+1)</strong></div>
										<div class="stat-row"><span>DEX</span><strong>6 (+3)</strong></div>
										<div class="stat-row"><span>CON</span><strong>2 (+1)</strong></div>
