										<div class="ability-header">
											<strong>Fang Jab</strong>
											<span class="ability-cost">1 Stamina • Melee (DEX)</span>
										</div>
										<p><strong>Attack:</strong> d20 + 4 | <strong>Damage:</strong> 1d4 + 2</p>
										<p><strong>On hit:</strong> Light Venom — Target makes a CON Save (DC 10) or gains Poisoned</p>
									</div>

									<div class="ability">
										<div class="ability-header">
											<strong>Camouflage Coil</strong>
											<span class="ability-cost">Passive</span>
										</div>
										<p>While not moving on its previous turn, the viper becomes Camouflaged:</p>
										<ul>
											<li>Hunters must pass an INS check (DC 10) to notice it</li>
											<li>First attack it makes from camouflage has advantage</li>
										</ul>
									</div>

									<div class="ability">
										<div class="ability-header">
											<strong>Startle Strike</strong>
											<span class="ability-cost">Reaction (1 Stamina)</span>
										</div>
										<p><strong>Trigger:</strong> A creature enters its space or steps adjacent without spotting it.</p>
										<p>The viper makes a free Fang Jab. This does not break camouflage until after the attack.</p>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>

