									</div>
									<div class="stat-block combat-stats">
										<div class="stat-row"><span>AR</span><strong>9</strong></div>
										<div class="stat-row"><span>HP</span><strong>70</strong></div>
										<div class="stat-row"><span>Stamina</span><strong>16</strong></div>
										<div class="stat-row"><span>Movement</span><strong>30 ft surface / 60 ft burrow</strong></div>
										<div class="stat-row"><span>Attacks/Turn</span><strong>2</strong></div>
										<div class="stat-row"><span>Stamina Drain</span><strong>-2/turn while burrowed</strong></div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="creature-section">
								<h4>🗡️ Attacks & Abilities</h4>
								<div class="ability-list">
									<div class="ability">
										<div class="ability-header">
											<strong>Claw Swipe</strong>
											<span class="ability-cost">1 Stamina • Melee (STR)</span>
										</div>
										<p><strong>Attack:</strong> d20 + 5 | <strong>Damage:</strong> 1d8 + 3</p>
										<p>On failed DEX save (DC 10): Target is knocked back 5 ft.</p>
									</div>

									<div class="ability">
										<div class="ability-header">
